O + SiteOrigin</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-limiting-the-modified-date-in-thrive-architect-and-siteorigin\">Limiting the Modified Date in Thrive Architect and SiteOrigin</a></li></ul></div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<iframe title=\"Announcing Full Support For Thrive Architect &amp; Site Origin Page Builders!\" width=\"500\" height=\"281\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/YKBcAkvsNkQ?feature=oembed&#038;rel=0\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n</div></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-aioseo-thrive-architect\">AIOSEO + Thrive Architect</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Thrive Architect is fast becoming one of the most popular page builders among WordPress users. This is mainly thanks to its super-intuitive interface and powerful visual builder. If youâ€™re one of its fans, youâ€™ll be glad to know that Thrive Architect now supports AIOSEO right inside its dashboard. As you edit your pages, you can now find the AIOSEO button in the top right corner of the page builder.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1002\" height=\"497\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/aioseo-thrive-1.png\" alt=\"Accessing AIOSEO in Thrive Architect.\" class=\"wp-image-352850\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/aioseo-thrive-1.png 1002w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/aioseo-thrive-1-300x149.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/aioseo-thrive-1-768x381.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/aioseo-thrive-1-600x298.png 600w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The AIOSEO button features your TruSEO score, allowing you to quickly see how well youâ€™ve optimized your page.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Clicking on the button will open a menu with AIOSEO settings.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1002\" height=\"445\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/aioseo-settings-in-thrive-architect.png\" alt=\"AIOSEO settings in Thrive Architect.\" class=\"wp-image-352852\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/aioseo-settings-in-thrive-architect.png 1002w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/aioseo-settings-in-thrive-architect-300x133.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/aioseo-settings-in-thrive-architect-768x341.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/aioseo-settings-in-thrive-architect-600x266.png 600w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>You can select any menu item depending on what you want to optimize on that page. The beauty of this is that TruSEO also works right from within the page builder!&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"902\" height=\"556\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/aioseo-truseo-in-thrive-architect.png\" alt=\"AIOSEO\'s TruSEO in Thrive Architect.\" class=\"wp-image-352853\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/aioseo-truseo-in-thrive-architect.png 902w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/aioseo-truseo-in-thrive-architect-300x185.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/aioseo-truseo-in-thrive-architect-768x473.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/aioseo-truseo-in-thrive-architect-600x370.png 600w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>This means you can work on your on-page SEO on the fly, reducing the time needed to optimize your site.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Alternatively, you can also access the AIOSEO settings by clicking the WordPress icon in the side menu:</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"462\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/aioseo-in-thrive-architect-wordpress-menu-1024x462.png\" alt=\"aioseo in thrive architect wordpress-menu\" class=\"wp-image-352854\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/aioseo-in-thrive-architect-wordpress-menu-1024x462.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/aioseo-in-thrive-architect-wordpress-menu-300x135.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/aioseo-in-thrive-architect-wordpress-menu-768x346.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/aioseo-in-thrive-architect-wordpress-menu-600x271.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/aioseo-in-thrive-architect-wordpress-menu.png 1102w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Doing so will open a menu with many WordPress settings, including the AIOSEO integration:</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"532\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/aioseo-in-wordpress-settings-1024x532.png\" alt=\"aioseo-in-wordpress-settings\" class=\"wp-image-352855\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/aioseo-in-wordpress-settings-1024x532.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/aioseo-in-wordpress-settings-300x156.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/aioseo-in-wordpress-settings-768x399.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/aioseo-in-wordpress-settings-600x311.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/aioseo-in-wordpress-settings.png 1202w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Ranking your pages has become easier as you can now implement SEO best practices right from within Thrive Architect!&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-aioseo-siteorigin\"><strong>AIOSEO + SiteOrigin</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Weâ€™ve also added an integration for SiteOrigin users that makes it easy to optimize your page as you build it. This means you can publish new content or update existing pages much faster.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The AIOSEO button is at the top left-hand side of the SiteOrigin toolbar.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"361\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/aioseo-button-in-site-origin-1024x361.png\" alt=\"AIOSEO in the SiteOrigin page builder.\" class=\"wp-image-352858\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/aioseo-button-in-site-origin-1024x361.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/aioseo-button-in-site-origin-300x106.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/aioseo-button-in-site-origin-768x271.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/aioseo-button-in-site-origin-600x212.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/aioseo-button-in-site-origin.png 1202w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Clicking on the AIOSEO button will open a menu with many of the AIOSEO settings youâ€™re familiar with and love.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1002\" height=\"442\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/aioseo-settings-in-site-origin-1.png\" alt=\"AIOSEO settings in SiteOrigin.\" class=\"wp-image-352859\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/aioseo-settings-in-site-origin-1.png 1002w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/aioseo-settings-in-site-origin-1-300x132.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/aioseo-settings-in-site-origin-1-768x339.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/aioseo-settings-in-site-origin-1-600x265.png 600w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>This means you can optimize many aspects of your pages and posts right from within the page builder. Examples of SEO settings youâ€™ll find include:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>General SEO settings</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Social settings</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Schema settings</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Redirects settings</li>\n\n\n\n<li>SEO Revisions</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Advanced settings</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>You can even use the powerful TruSEO Analyzer right inside SiteOrigin. All these features enable you to easily optimize your page on the fly with AIOSEOâ€™s suggestions.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you love the SiteOrigin page builder, then youâ€™ll love it more when you experience the powerful combination of your favorite page builder and the worldâ€™s best SEO plugin.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-limiting-the-modified-date-in-thrive-architect-and-siteorigin\">Limiting the Modified Date in Thrive Architect and SiteOrigin</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Another handy feature youâ€™ll love with our page builder integrations is the ability to limit the modified date when you edit existing posts or pages.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Once you finish your edits, you can prevent the update from changing the published date to the day you made the changes.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1002\" height=\"456\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/limit-modified-date.png\" alt=\"Limiting the last modified date.\" class=\"wp-image-352861\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/limit-modified-date.png 1002w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/limit-modified-date-300x137.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/limit-modified-date-768x350.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/limit-modified-date-600x273.png 600w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>This is particularly helpful when you make minor changes to your posts or pages and donâ€™t want to signal the change to users and search engines. Limiting the last modified date also prevents the page from being moved to the top of your sitemap.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Having AIOSEO work in your page builder gives you more control and flexibility when optimizing your site. This is a game changer for those using Thrive Architect and SiteOrigin.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Besides Thrive Architect and SiteOrigin, we also have integrations with:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/features/seedprod-and-aioseo-integration/\" title=\"SeedProd and AIOSEO Integration\">SeedProd</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/features/divi-and-aioseo-integration/\" title=\"Divi and AIOSEO Integration\">Divi</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/features/elementor-and-aioseo-integration/\" title=\"Elementor and AIOSEO Integration\">Elementor</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/features/wpbakery-and-aioseo-integration/\" title=\"WPBakery and AIOSEO Integration\">WPBakery</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/features/avada-and-aioseo-integration/\" title=\"Avada and AIOSEO Integration\">Avada</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Our ultimate goal is for AIOSEO to integrate seamlessly with all your favorite page builders.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Besides these page builder integrations, weâ€™ve also improved many other features in the plugin.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You can see all our changes in our <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/changelog/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"Changelog\">full product changelog</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>What are you waiting for?&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Update your site to AIOSEO 4.6.6 to unlock these powerful new features and rank your content higher on SERPs.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>And if youâ€™re not yet using AIOSEO, make sure to <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/docs/installing-all-in-one-seo-pro/\" title=\"Installing All in One SEO Pro\">install and activate the plugin today</a>.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you have questions about these features, please comment below or <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/contact/\" title=\"Contact Us\">contact our customer support team</a>. Weâ€™re always ready to help. Our commitment to making AIOSEO the easiest and best WordPress SEO plugin is only getting stronger as we continue to win as a team with you, our customers.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Weâ€™re so grateful for your continued support, feedback, and suggestions. Please keep those suggestions and feature requests coming!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>We hope you enjoy using these new SEO features as much as we enjoyed creating them.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><em>-Benjamin Rojas (President of AIOSEO).</em></p>The post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/new-support-for-thrive-architect-and-siteorigin-page-builders/\">Optimize Faster with AIOSEO 4.6.6: New Support for Thrive Architect and SiteOrigin Page Builders</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:86:\"https://aioseo.com/new-support-for-thrive-architect-and-siteorigin-page-builders/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"2\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:3;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:76:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n					\n			\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:65:\"Beginnerâ€™s Guide to Content Optimization for SEO [2024 Edition]\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:104:\"https://aioseo.com/content-optimization/?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=content-optimization\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";